==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: nemertine
<hw>nemertine</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any of an order
(<ord>Nemertina</ord>) of soft unsegmented marine worms having an
reversible threadlike proboscis and the ability to stretch and
contract.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> ribbon worm, nemertean, proboscis worm.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nemesis</ent>⟦br⟧
